---
id: hello
name: "Hello World"
version: 1.0.0
description: "A simple greeting prompt"
parameters:
  - name: name
    type: string
    required: true
    description: "The name to greet"
    default: "World"
---

# Hello, {{ name }}!

Write a short, friendly greeting for someone named {{ name }}. Keep it to 2-3 sentences.
